### Figure Data ###############

There is a directory for each figure and supplementary figure containing 
all processed data used to generate the figures.

### Additional Data and Scripts ###############

Further data, software input files, and analysis scripts are provided
in the following directories.


HiP-HoP_Pax6_FullConformations		Contains the full set of simulated
					Pax6 locus conformations as used in 
					Fig. 5 and Videos 3-5.

ExampleSimulationInputScripts		Contains a set of input data and all
					input files and scripts used to run a 
					HiP-HoP simulation.

